proteo (0.1.1) resolute; urgency=medium

  * Fix multi-second stream lag: the EVDI holder now consumes frames
    (register buffer + request_update + grab_pixels). A non-draining client
    left KWin's flips on the virtual output uncompleted, delaying every
    composited/screencast frame. Verified ~58 fps drained on a 60 Hz mode.
  * contrib/steam-bigpicture.sh: watchdog launcher for Sunshine's Steam Big
    Picture app — retries steam://open/bigpicture until the window exists,
    then raises it past KWin focus-stealing prevention.

 -- Italo Piscopiello <piscopiello.italo@gmail.com>  Mon, 06 Jul 2026 09:30:00 +0200

proteo (0.1.0) resolute; urgency=medium

  * Initial release: client-matched virtual displays for Sunshine/Apollo on
    KDE Plasma Wayland + AMD. do/undo/status/rescue CLI, EVDI holder as
    transient systemd user unit, proteo-guard failsafe daemon (host/holder
    watch, sleep inhibitor), CVT-RB EDID generation.

 -- Italo Piscopiello <piscopiello.italo@gmail.com>  Sun, 05 Jul 2026 17:00:00 +0200
